HEADWORD: Hellier
<hw>Hel"li*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Hele</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <def>One who heles or covers; hence, a tiler,
slater, or thatcher.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>heler</asp>.]</altsp> <rj><au>Usher.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
